Marrakech,0NkAE4N8E1A,Ugw04c9i-orrlBYiNj14AaABAg,,@DLPdiaries,"Marrakech is so amazing! We stayed in a Riad in the Medina and did excursions to the Atlas mountains (blew our mind, so beautiful!), Essouira and a quad tour through the palmeraie. And of course wandered through the medina, had the best food and experiences in the gardens and djamaa El Fna etc. I would realy reccomend visiting. The Moroccans are SO welcoming and kind! You do need to keep in mind to haggle in the shops, and not fall for the monkey scams on the square or ' i'll show you the way' scams but other than that...such amazing people and such a beautiful culture!",2025-08-20T14:34:30Z,2025-08-20T14:35:17Z,6,False,0.0,2026-05-18T02:01:19.468815
