Marrakech,05QDGvi0_sM,UgyXcBbYI5UvzNHWpud4AaABAg.AM1vhYUXWaZAM8SRBCFxcw,UgyXcBbYI5UvzNHWpud4AaABAg,@96Caleb96,"​​@FindingGinaMarieThankyou very much! Atleast i know not to fully rely on it, will try and use landmarks and comms instead!",2025-08-22T20:40:09Z,2025-08-22T21:14:27Z,0,True,,2026-05-18T02:01:26.843497
Marrakech,05QDGvi0_sM,UgyXcBbYI5UvzNHWpud4AaABAg.AM1vhYUXWaZAM8WTfayjJm,UgyXcBbYI5UvzNHWpud4AaABAg,@FindingGinaMarie,"Yes, paying close attention to landmarks helps a lot, and we tried to use the same paths as often as we could. It's challenging when you want to explore, because you can go deep and find yourself in a maze where everything starts to look the same! Some people suggest having a walking tour to help you navigate, but we seemed to figure it out okay on our own. By the time we did a walking tour, we had become pretty comfortable navigating it on our own. —Judy",2025-08-22T21:15:27Z,2025-08-22T21:15:27Z,1,True,,2026-05-18T02:01:26.843500
