Marrakech,05QDGvi0_sM,Ugyi8wtoOXUiYFwy2l54AaABAg.AI9MqxLo2vTAIBwKV4v3rJ,Ugyi8wtoOXUiYFwy2l54AaABAg,@CelticMickTravels,"​@FindingGinaMarieThanks, I was a bit worried but saw loads of content and less afraid of filming 😂😂",2025-05-16T19:02:16Z,2025-05-16T19:02:16Z,0,True,,2026-05-18T02:01:28.221768
Marrakech,05QDGvi0_sM,Ugyi8wtoOXUiYFwy2l54AaABAg.AI9MqxLo2vTAIBwoCIUwfA,Ugyi8wtoOXUiYFwy2l54AaABAg,@FindingGinaMarie,"@CelticMickTravels Just be mindful that people don't always want to be photographed/filmed. There were a few people who made it very clear to us that they did not want to be in any pictures or videos! Some of it is tied to religion, but there definitely are sensitivities there. We tried to ask first as much as possible. —Judy",2025-05-16T19:06:28Z,2025-05-16T19:06:28Z,1,True,,2026-05-18T02:01:28.221770
Marrakech,05QDGvi0_sM,UgygZU6QQK-K6GiPyIt4AaABAg.AI8sQf1RvHxAI90MngF_zh,UgygZU6QQK-K6GiPyIt4AaABAg,@FindingGinaMarie,"Hi Tim, That's awesome. His jokes were a bit corny at times, but he gave some great information. One suggestion is that if you want to haggle somewhere, you need to ask him for guidance before you get there in order to not put him in a tough spot. Have a great time. Here are our other videos from our 40+ days in Morocco! —Judy
