Marrakech,YRzBoL2qhp8,UgxQT_b7SkbOvaDmoU14AaABAg.AFBNgk7R9HbAFCRQ011wP1,UgxQT_b7SkbOvaDmoU14AaABAg,@ReigneOrShine,"Thank you so much for watching and appreciating our video. My boots are from Dr Martens. Been using it for almost 7 years and they are still in good condition even when it gets wet or un very dry place. I used it in the Sahara. But I take slightly bigger than my size to make space because if it’s just right size, it can be sore on the toes.",2025-03-03T10:08:28Z,2025-03-03T10:08:28Z,0,True,,2026-05-18T02:01:38.240988
