Tanger,MnpgsP46tGk,UgyDCS1iK-U9pSsLf9Z4AaABAg,,@fiesta86m,Um so yeah so i found this song on my fyp randomly on around oct 15th 2025 and after that i feel like i've experienced all sorts of music i ever listened to in some new way after going through your tracks idk really how to describe this tbh. But this is really cool i've been listening to the whole album for a while now and every time when it gets to this exact song i just feel all the possible emotions at once. It's been kinda though time recently for me and i don't really know what i should do but hey after encountering you i now feel way more motivated? i guess. I barely know you and you don't know me at all but i feel like you're a really nice person. I hope this comment makes your day a bit happier and give a bit more motivation to keep doing what you love,2026-02-27T20:52:17Z,2026-02-27T20:52:17Z,3,False,0.0,2026-05-18T02:03:22.828285
